    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies a new Port Control Protocol (PCP) functional element: the PCP proxy.  The PCP proxy relays PCP requests received from PCP clients to upstream PCP server(s).  A typical deployment usage of this function is to help establish successful PCP communications for PCP clients that cannot be configured with the address of a PCP server located more than one hop away.
	 </t>
